The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect clickbait headlines. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The use of attention layers and image embeddings suggests the involvement of deep learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques as well.
